        <img alt="image_69.png" border-effect="rounded" src="image_69.png"/>
        <p>Now on GitHub, we can see that the file was correctly pushed: </p>
        <img alt="image_70.png" border-effect="rounded" src="image_70.png"/>
    </procedure>
